{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-item-js","path":"/projects/ondrej-chrastina-tech","result":{"data":{"kontentItemProject":{"system":{"id":"e8417761-bdad-47f8-bd18-f51eb8373220"},"elements":{"title":{"value":"ondrej.chrastina.tech"},"release_date":{"value":"2020-08-22T00:00:00Z"},"source_code_url":{"value":"https://github.com/Simply007/Simply007.github.io"},"live_url":{"value":"https://ondrej.chrastina.tech"},"summary":{"value":"<p>My personal website build with <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/\">Gatsby</a> and <a href=\"https://app.kontent.ai\">Kentico Kontent</a> as a data source.</p>"},"image":{"value":[{"url":"https://assets-eu-01.kc-usercontent.com:443/75653ec1-36a2-01e0-0d25-a64799947697/59bed03f-18b7-437a-978a-254f6cb9cd15/og-image[1].png","width":1200,"height":600,"description":null}]},"content":{"value":"<p>This website was initially built as many dev's websites (Aug 2020) - the POC to test out the technology.<br>\nThis particular trial was based on <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/starters/codebushi/gatsby-starter-forty\">Forty Gatsby Starter</a>, but it turned out to be pretty nice and complex. So I have decided to use it production so to speak. With CSS Grid support, all tooling set up including SCSS configuration, &nbsp;prepared <a href=\"https://fontawesome.com/icons\">icons using Font Awesome</a>, embedded style guide made it the great candidate to connect to <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/@kentico/gatsby-source-kontent/\">Kentico Kontent using the integration with Gatsby.js</a> I have been working on at that time.</p>\n<figure data-asset-id=\"12777113-75cb-4143-ad5c-bbeba89b5554\" data-image-id=\"12777113-75cb-4143-ad5c-bbeba89b5554\"><img src=\"https://assets-eu-01.kc-usercontent.com:443/75653ec1-36a2-01e0-0d25-a64799947697/59bed03f-18b7-437a-978a-254f6cb9cd15/og-image[1].png\" data-asset-id=\"12777113-75cb-4143-ad5c-bbeba89b5554\" data-image-id=\"12777113-75cb-4143-ad5c-bbeba89b5554\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n<p><br>\nDuring the time I have done some extensions, but mostly content-wise, as you might have noticed from my explicit listing of design predefinitions of the starter. To mention some. I have added a categories filter for the listing pages, then the \"Projects\" section - the one that this page is in, and a new navigation content structure to follow <a href=\"http://webspotlight.kontent.ai/\">Kontent Web Spotlight</a> feature needs.<br>\n</p>\n<figure data-asset-id=\"8d9fcbad-6851-4510-a046-a6e1959274b5\" data-image-id=\"8d9fcbad-6851-4510-a046-a6e1959274b5\"><img src=\"https://assets-eu-01.kc-usercontent.com:443/75653ec1-36a2-01e0-0d25-a64799947697/4b058346-69f5-464b-8f39-1c8b4ac5c4b8/personal-site-webspotlight.png\" data-asset-id=\"8d9fcbad-6851-4510-a046-a6e1959274b5\" data-image-id=\"8d9fcbad-6851-4510-a046-a6e1959274b5\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n<p><br></p>","modular_content":[],"images":[{"image_id":"12777113-75cb-4143-ad5c-bbeba89b5554","url":"https://assets-eu-01.kc-usercontent.com:443/75653ec1-36a2-01e0-0d25-a64799947697/59bed03f-18b7-437a-978a-254f6cb9cd15/og-image[1].png","width":1200,"height":600,"description":null},{"image_id":"8d9fcbad-6851-4510-a046-a6e1959274b5","url":"https://assets-eu-01.kc-usercontent.com:443/75653ec1-36a2-01e0-0d25-a64799947697/4b058346-69f5-464b-8f39-1c8b4ac5c4b8/personal-site-webspotlight.png","width":2880,"height":1725,"description":null}]}}}},"pageContext":{"language":"en-US","codename":"ondrej_chrastina_tech"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2624379000","690649307"]}